/**
 * Embedded webfonts for the weekly-report PDF (server-only — imported
 * exclusively by /api/reports/pdf). Geist (variable, 400-700) + Fraunces
 * (variable, 600-700), latin + latin-ext subsets, inlined as data URIs so
 * PDF rendering is hermetic: no runtime fetch to Google Fonts, no
 * proxy/CA surprises, the same embedded fonts in every environment.
 *
 * Generated from https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,600;9..144,700&family=Geist:wght@400;600;700
 * (both fonts are OFL-licensed). Regenerate by re-fetching that stylesheet
 * with a woff2-capable User-Agent and inlining each url() as base64.
 */

